<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#008000">(١٢)</span> بَابُ الصَّلَاةِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">س ١١٦:</span> مَا مَعْنَى الصَّلَاةِ؟<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">الصَّلَاةُ:</span> هِيَ التَّعَبُّدُ للهِ تَعَالَى بِأَقْوَالٍ وَأَفْعَالٍ مَخْصُوصَةٍ، مُفْتَتَحَةٍ بِالتَّكْبِيرِ، وَمُخْتَتَمَةٍ بِالتَّسْلِيمِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>* * *<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">س ١١٧:</span> مَا الصَّلَوَاتُ الْمَفْرُوضَةُ الْوَاجِبَةُ عَلَى كُلِّ مُسْلِمٍ وَمُسْلِمَةٍ؟<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>الصَّلَوَاتُ الْمَفْرُوضَةُ خَمْسُ صَلَوَاتٍ فِي الْيَوْمِ وَاللَّيْلَةِ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١ - الْفَجْرُ <span style="color:#008000">(رَكْعَتَانِ)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٢ - الظُّهْرُ <span style="color:#008000">(أَرْبَعُ رَكَعَاتٍ)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٣ - الْعَصْرُ <span style="color:#008000">(أَرْبَعُ رَكَعَاتٍ)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٤ - الْمَغْرِبُ <span style="color:#008000">(ثَلَاثُ رَكَعَاتٍ)</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٥ - الْعِشَاءُ <span style="color:#008000">(أَرْبَعُ رَكَعَاتٍ)</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>* * *<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>